Like Tom, I feel a desire to sit back and read.  It is good to see you here Paul..  It means that the word is still out there.  What happened to me is I found myself responding in many cases with sarcasm to posts that were sincere.  That was where I was prior to seeking help.  I don't wish to go back there.  On the other hand, having read some of my other posts, it sure sounded stuffy, pontificating and aloof from the processes going on here. <br>
So, like Tom, I come and go.  I used to eagerly scan here for new messages and thoughts.  Now I just drop by to say &quot;Hi&quot;.  Cook, SW, MTF, Art, you guys have a real thing going here. Communication takes place and things happen. It's good to see new names in the mix. It opens up new lines of communication. (See what I mean!)  Sheesh, didn't mean to do that. But, the fact remains, time to close this part out and check out other things.  Stopping by occasionally and dropping my two cents.<br>
I hope everyone has enough crayons and paper. Drive on, guys!<br>
Chet   ..Spameater six,out!
